{
  "texts": [
    "We chose this library due to its proven effectiveness in retrieving relevant applications in various domains, such as ecology and evolution (Lortie et al. 2020).",
    "This search yielded 329 tools, which we then evaluated using the same two-stage selection process previously applied for the tools produced by searching the SLR Toolbox.",
    "However, none of these tools incorporated AI solutions while also providing a visual interface.",
    "Consequently, we discarded all of them.",
    "After deduplicating the results from the SLR toolbox and previous surveys, we identified 17 tools linked to research papers and 8 tools without associated papers."
  ]
}